00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,600
Wala akong sinabi.

490
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:41,680
Pull over sa pharmacy.

491
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:44,800
Ano ang problema?

492
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:45,960
Kunin mo ako ng gamot.

493
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:47,440
Anong gamot?

494
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,840
Isang bagay na
nakakapagpababa ng libido ko.

495
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:55,920
Hindi ito gagawin.

496
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,680
May kailangan akong isipin.

497
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,920
Sukat 80.

498
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:06,000
Sukat 82.1.

499
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:09,520
Ito ay...

500
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:11,800
Xiao Tian.

501
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:14,599
Nakarating na kami ni Chi Cheng sa
Shengshi Club.

502
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:16,840
- Kailan ka darating?
- Shengshi Club?

503
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:18,799
pasensya na po. Nagkamali ako nagpadala.

504
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:19,880
Nagpadala siya ng hindi sinasadya?

505
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,160
Darn it.

506
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:25,440
Pumunta ulit siya doon.

507
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,800
Alam kong hindi niya
ito kakayanin.

508
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:30,000
Yung pervert na mutt!

509
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:32,320
Papatayin ko siya!

510
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,200
Mr. Chi.

511
00:33:44,840 --> 00:33:46,520
Diba sabi mo
may kliyente akong gustong makita...

512
00:33:46,560 --> 00:33:48,040
mag-order ng ilang art installation?

513
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:49,160
Bakit mo ako dinala dito?

514
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,759
Malapit nang dumating ang kliyente.

515
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:52,880
Magsaya muna tayo.

516
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:03,480
Young Master Chi,
sa wakas nandito ka na.

517
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,200
Magwala.

518
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:07,560
Young Master Chi, sinipa niya ako.

519
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,280
Young Master Chi.

520
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:15,320
Sasampalin ko siya pag-uwi namin.

521
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,680
Makinig kayong lahat!

522
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,399
Mula ngayon,

523
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:27,720
magpapaalam na tayo sa lugar na ito
magpakailanman.

524
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:31,200
Ikinalulungkot ko na hindi ko na sinusuportahan
ang iyong negosyo.

525
00:34:31,640 --> 00:34:32,959
Sinong gustong makita siya?

526
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:34,320
Tingnan mong mabuti.

527
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,400
Nang makalabas na siya sa pintong ito,

528
00:34:35,401 --> 00:34:37,080
hindi ka na magkakaroon ng pagkakataon
na tingnan siya muli.

529
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:41,840
Ano ang ibig sabihin nito?

530
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:44,240
Umuwi na tayo at kumuha ng certificate.

531
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:50,000
Nakakabahala talaga pag lumabas ka
ng walang certificate sa panahon ngayon.

532
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:18,760
saan tayo?

533
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,200
Ang bago kong tahanan.

534
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:23,360
Gayunpaman...

535
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:34,400
Ito ay magiging
iyong bagong tahanan sa lalong madaling panahon,

536
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:36,680
ang aking munting amo.
